dct_title_s: Hartfordshire described : the sittuations of Hartford, and the most ancient towne S. Albons with such memorable actions as have happened
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Insets: Hartforde -- Verolanium. Shows hundreds and main roads. Date of publication from Chubb. From: England fully described in a compleat sett of mapps ... London : Printed & sold by Henry Overton ... , 1743.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Sold by Henry Overton at the White Horse without Newgate, [1743]
